snippet.title: HIGHEST LEVEL of FUNNINESS! - BURST into LAUGHTER NOW!
snippet.description:
Animals are so super hilarious, they make us laugh all the time! You are never bored watching animal videos, they never fail to make us smile and happy. here are the best and the funniest animal videos! The hardest try not to laugh challenge! Just look how all these dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, pig, sheep, ferret... behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things and more! So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!

The content in this compilation is licensed and used with authorization of the rights holder. If you have any questions about compilation or clip licensing, please contact us: tigerlicensing@gmail.com

For more funny videos & pictures visit and like our Facebook page:
https://www.facebook.com/tigerstudiosfun

MUSIC:
"Monkeys Spinnin Monkeys" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)

Artist: http://audionautix.com/
